column5: Just wondering if you decided to cross the border for a Clam?   If you did what did customs say?

well i decided to bring my fishing stuff and hit a couple of lake erie tribs and on my way back i hit gander mountain and picked it up...took it out of the box and threw it in the back of my truck and hid it under all my fishing equipment with no questions asked wonder if i can hide a new atv in my truck bed
